Weblogic stop process
======================
10.82.156.177

1] Stop Manage server from console.

Domain Structure → Environment → Servers 

Click on the Control tab (top)
Select the checkbox next to the Managed Server you want to shop
Click Shutdown → choose Force shutdown now
Click Yes to confirm

2] stop Node manager from server end:
10.82.156.177

